<paragraph blockId="174.[264,1323,1793,1899]" pageId="174" pageNumber="175">
This specific name is from Latin &quot; 
<emphasis box="[727,811,1833,1858]" italics="true" pageId="174" pageNumber="175">lautus&quot;</emphasis>
meaning elegant or neat, and refers to the shiny, bare abdominal dorsum.
</paragraph>
